These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, electronic, rock, blues
1. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of blues##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of rock##1
3. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | rock | electronic | metal | blues |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, rat, pony
1. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | ferret | rat | hamster | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, drawing, video-games, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | video-games | fishing | drawing | sudoku |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, quad-bike, airplane, boat
1. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Transport   | airplane | subway | quad-bike | boat |

 #################################

 
