1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3       |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | western | superhero | fantasy |

